        MessageAccessor.MessageFilter inRange(int start,
                                      int end)
        Get all the top-level messages affected by the events between (and including) "start" en "end". A top-level message may have been added, or a message may have been changed by a progress update or a new child message, or by a change of any of its already contained child messages.
